OL,3,CFire fighters battle hay shed blaze
OL,4,Cfor 14 hours
OL,6,FA large fire at a hay shed in Co Down
OL,7,Fhas been extinguished after
OL,8,Ffirefighters battled it for more than
OL,9,F14 hours.
OL,11,FAround 300 sheep and 30 calves were
OL,12,Fmoved out of the shed on Cascum Road
OL,13,Fin Banbridge, while efforts continued
OL,14,Fto extinguish the fire.
OL,16,FMore than 40 firefighters were
OL,17,Ftackling the fire at its height.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
