OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775495152
OL,3,CFire fighters battle hay shed blaze
OL,4,Cfor 14 hours
OL,6,FThe cause of the fire is believed to
OL,7,Fbe accidental, according to a
OL,8,Fspokeswoman for the Northern Ireland
OL,9,FFire & Rescue Service (NIFRS).
OL,11,F"The initial call was received at
OL,12,F9.03pm, Thursday 2 April 2026," NIFRS
OL,13,Farea commander Suzanne Fleming said
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Initially, 300 sheep in the shed were
OL,17,Fled to safety by NIFRS Large Animal
OL,18,FRescue Team from Newcastle."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@_O]xD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
