PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775495152
OL,3,CFire fighters battle hay shed blaze
OL,4,Cfor 14 hours
OL,6,FIn a statement issued at 6am, she said
OL,7,Fthe fire was in the hay, which was
OL,8,Fbeing removed by a telehandler.
OL,10,FShe said more than 40 firefighters and
OL,11,Fsix fire appliances, including a water
OL,12,Ftanker from Warrenpoint Fire Station
OL,13,Fand a Command Support Unit from
OL,14,FLisburn Fire Station, had worked
OL,15,Fthroughout the night to bring it under
OL,16,Fcontrol.
OL,18,FThe fire was extinguished at 11.50am,
OL,19,Fthe NIFRS spokeswoman said.
